    <p>Height: 1.75m Weight: 87kg</p>
    <p>Ex­er­cise reg­i­men: I train al­most every day, ex­cept on week­ends, de­pend­ing on my sched­ule. I train each mus­cle group twice a week.</p>
    <p>Diet: I eat six to seven meals daily and pack my own meals to work. Dur­ing the off-sea­son, I am not too strict with my diet but will al­ways keep it bal­anced. I also make sure my body fat per­cent­age is not too high.</p>

